This is a description of the FAQ files, and how to submit the faq


Files:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

There are three files here:

README
------

   This file.

beta-language-faq.html
----------------------

   HTML source code for the BETA FAQ. 

   This is the file to make changes in.

beta-language-faq.txt
---------------------

   Textual version of BETA FAQ (may not be up-to-date). 

   Derived from beta-language-faq.html as follows:

   0) Make sure ~beta/public_html/doc/faq/beta-language-faq.html is up-to-date:

         cd ~beta/public_html/doc/faq/
         cvs update

   1a) Start Netscape (v2.0 or newer) using:
         netscape ...faq-file.html...

        and do the following:
   1b) Click "Save As..." button.
   1c) Choose "Text" as format for saved document.
   1d) Specify "beta-language-faq.txt" as name for saved document.
   1e) Click "OK".

   2) Manually change Danish {\oe} and Swedish \"{o} to "o".

   3) Check result in under cvs:

         cvs commit beta-language-faq.txt

   4) After checking in, copy file to 

         DAIMI: 
		cd /home/ftp/pub/beta/faq/
		cp /users/beta/public_html/doc/faq/beta-language-faq.txt .
         Log ind på noatun.mjolner.dk som beta.: 
		cd /export/ftp/ftp/pub
		rcp daimi.aau.dk:/users/beta/public_html/doc/faq/beta-language-faq.txt .

      to update the info at the official ftp sites.


If Netscape does not work properly in 1a)-1e), you can use the
 old method: Start Mosaic using the command line

         Mosaic http://www.daimi.aau.dk/~beta/doc/faq/beta-language-faq.html -xrm 'Mosaic*font: 8x13' -xrm 'Mosaic*italicFont: 8x13' -xrm 'Mosaic*boldFont: 8x13' -xrm 'Mosaic*fixedFont: 8x13' -geometry 70x50

   1b) Click "Save As..." button.
   1c) Choose "Plain Text" as format for saved document (probably default).
   1d) Specify "beta-language-faq.txt" as name for saved document.
   1e) Click "OK".

   2a) Manually change Danish {\oe} and Swedish \"{o} to "o".
   2b) Manually break about a dozen lines longer than 70 chars 
       (Mosaic*boldFont directive doesn't seem to work?!).

Submitting to the newsgroups:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Submitting to the newsgroups are done by following the following steps:

1) login as jlk@daimi.aau.dk, who is the authorized sender of the faq.
   If anybody have to post it, a mail saying so most be send to 
	?newsgroup-request? (* jeg kan ikke lige nu huske det :-( *)
   Other changes to the distribution etc., must be informed the same way
   (and an acceptance mail should be recieved) before the change may take
   effect.

2) invoke
	nnpost

3) specify comp.lang.beta as the newsgroup, and distribution: world

4) In the editor, 
   a) Remove the original text
   b) Insert the file:
	   beta-language-faq.header,
      and  beta-language-faq.txt
      immediately after each others.

   c) Follow the instructions, enclosed in << and >> uodating dates and
      versions.

   d) Remove the lines with << >>

   e) exit the editor, saving the changes.

5) view the message before posting.

6) Post it !!!

7) Update the version numbers to make beta-language-faq.html ready
   for next release, and update the 'Changed since last release sections,
   removing the current entries, and commit these changes.

8) Update THIS FILE if you have experienced and errors or omissions
   while using this description.  Commit the changes, if any.
